00:36:23,599 --> 00:36:24,539
[SPEAKER_00] u njihovim plemenima,

669
00:36:24,539 --> 00:36:25,840
[SPEAKER_00] očevu braću,

670
00:36:25,840 --> 00:36:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] što bi smo rekli stričevi,

671
00:36:27,159 --> 00:36:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] zovu očevi.

672
00:36:28,940 --> 00:36:31,300
[SPEAKER_00] Očevu braću zovu isto očevi,

673
00:36:31,300 --> 00:36:31,699
[SPEAKER_00] tate.

674
00:36:31,699 --> 00:36:33,739
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da oni smiju imati više tate,

675
00:36:33,739 --> 00:36:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] a ne samo jednog.

676
00:36:34,599 --> 00:36:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] Evo,

677
00:36:35,539 --> 00:36:36,860
[SPEAKER_00] gospodine radođe na aparatima.

678
00:36:36,860 --> 00:36:37,760
[SPEAKER_00] I,

679
00:36:37,760 --> 00:36:40,699
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

680
00:36:40,699 --> 00:36:43,019
[SPEAKER_00] majčine sestre zovu majke.

681
00:36:43,019 --> 00:36:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ne zovu ih tete,

682
00:36:44,920 --> 00:36:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje,

683
00:36:45,619 --> 00:36:45,860
[SPEAKER_00] i to,

684
00:36:45,860 --> 00:36:46,880
[SPEAKER_00] nego isto zovu,

685
00:36:46,880 --> 00:36:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] isto i zovu majke.

686
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:48,780
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

687
00:36:48,780 --> 00:36:50,059
[SPEAKER_00] i naravno,

688
00:36:50,059 --> 00:36:51,159
[SPEAKER_00] jednom židovom koji je ovo čitao,

689
00:36:51,159 --> 00:36:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je vrlo jasna stvar.

690
00:36:52,460 --> 00:36:53,659
[SPEAKER_00] Drugo,

691
00:36:53,659 --> 00:36:55,320
[SPEAKER_00] još jedna činjenica.

692
00:36:55,320 --> 00:36:55,639
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo,

693
00:36:55,639 --> 00:36:57,599
[SPEAKER_00] zemije cezarejski,

694
00:36:58,119 --> 00:36:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] u svojoj, dakle,

695
00:36:58,960 --> 00:37:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] crkvenoj povijesti,

696
00:37:00,019 --> 00:37:02,179
[SPEAKER_00] 3.11.1.2.1,

697
00:37:02,179 --> 00:37:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] kaže ovo.

698
00:37:02,960 --> 00:37:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] To smo čitali čak i prošle puta.

699
00:37:05,300 --> 00:37:07,460
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon Jakovljeva mučeništva,

700
00:37:07,460 --> 00:37:09,639
[SPEAKER_00] prvi biskup Jeruzalema,

701
00:37:09,639 --> 00:37:10,800
[SPEAKER_00] Isusev Bratić,

702
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] oni od gospodinovih apostole i učenika

703
00:37:13,480 --> 00:37:16,260
[SPEAKER_00] našli su se zajedno s onima koji su ljudski rečeno

704
00:37:16,260 --> 00:37:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] od gospodinove obitelji.

705
00:37:17,599 --> 00:37:19,360
[SPEAKER_00] I svi se posavjetovaše,

706
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:21,219
[SPEAKER_00] komi mi dali čast da naslijedi Jakova,

707
00:37:21,219 --> 00:37:22,639
[SPEAKER_00] i svi jednodušno odlučiše,

708
00:37:22,639 --> 00:37:24,800
[SPEAKER_00] da je upravo Šimun, sin Kleofe,

709
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:26,739
[SPEAKER_00] kojega je vađelja isto spominju,

710
00:37:27,019 --> 00:37:27,699
[SPEAKER_00] pročitali smo,

711
00:37:27,699 --> 00:37:29,780
[SPEAKER_00] dostojat biskupske stolice u Rimu,

712
00:37:29,780 --> 00:37:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ovo je Jeruzalema,

713
00:37:31,119 --> 00:37:32,719
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ovaj drugi brat.

714
00:37:32,719 --> 00:37:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] To je bio neki nepotizam tada.

715
00:37:34,920 --> 00:37:35,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo će to.

716
00:37:35,880 --> 00:37:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

717
00:37:36,619 --> 00:37:38,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje je bio, kako se kaže,

718
00:37:38,619 --> 00:37:39,820
[SPEAKER_00] spasiteljev rođak.

719
00:37:39,820 --> 00:37:40,840
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, zanimljivo,

720
00:37:40,840 --> 00:37:42,639
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje će kažiti spasiteljev brat.

721
00:37:42,639 --> 00:37:44,519
[SPEAKER_00] Spasiteljev rođak, Bratić.

722
00:37:44,519 --> 00:37:47,360
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Kleofa bijaše Josipov brat.

723
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:48,659
[SPEAKER_00] Morate znati još jednu stvar.

724
00:37:48,659 --> 00:37:51,019
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ovdje govorimo o maloj crkvi.

725
00:37:51,019 --> 00:37:54,219
[SPEAKER_00] Crkvi tek u začetku u tom smislu.

726
00:37:54,219 --> 00:37:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vidimo, svako je svakoga znao.

727
00:37:56,500 --> 00:37:59,260
[SPEAKER_00] Još iz Isusove obitelji su bili biskupi.

728
00:37:59,260 --> 00:38:01,280
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko je to još bila mala crkva,

729
00:38:01,280 --> 00:38:02,239
[SPEAKER_00] mala zajednica.

730
00:38:02,239 --> 00:38:03,800
[SPEAKER_00] I ovo kad, e,

731
00:38:03,800 --> 00:38:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] Zemljec je za reski piše o ovome.

732
00:38:05,300 --> 00:38:05,800
[SPEAKER_00] On je, dakle,

733
00:38:05,800 --> 00:38:07,980
[SPEAKER_00] iz trećega stoljeća pisat,

734
00:38:07,980 --> 00:38:09,019
[SPEAKER_00] crkveni povijesničar.

735
00:38:09,019 --> 00:38:10,840
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, svi su znali tko je tko.

736
00:38:10,920 --> 00:38:12,800
[SPEAKER_00] Znali bi za pravu Isusovu braću.

737
00:38:12,800 --> 00:38:14,260
[SPEAKER_00] Da su ona zaista postojala.

738
00:38:14,260 --> 00:38:17,820
[SPEAKER_00] I pravo je Isusove sajstre.

739
00:38:17,820 --> 00:38:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] Isto tako.

740
00:38:18,420 --> 00:38:19,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

741
00:38:19,199 --> 00:38:20,659
[SPEAKER_00] međutim,

742
00:38:20,659 --> 00:38:21,820
[SPEAKER_00] kada nastaje problem,

743
00:38:21,820 --> 00:38:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] problem nastaje kada se crkva počinje širiti,

744
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:27,340
[SPEAKER_00] kada to više nije neka mala jeruzalemska zajednica,

745
00:38:27,340 --> 00:38:29,400
[SPEAKER_00] u početke,

746
00:38:29,400 --> 00:38:31,940
[SPEAKER_00] u prvih nekoliko godina

747
00:38:31,940 --> 00:38:33,920
[SPEAKER_00] nakon Isusovu skrslučaju za šašća,

748
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:35,739
[SPEAKER_00] kada je vađelje

749
00:38:35,739 --> 00:38:37,300
[SPEAKER_00] i, dakle, radosna vijest

750
00:38:37,300 --> 00:38:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] iz židovskih okvira,

751
00:38:38,679 --> 00:38:41,320
[SPEAKER_00] koji ima ovo sve jasno što ja sada vam objašnjavam ovdje,

752
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] ulazi u poganski svijet,

753
00:38:43,539 --> 00:38:45,119
[SPEAKER_00] koji ima ništa nije jasno

754
00:38:45,119 --> 00:38:46,699
[SPEAKER_00] i koji, naravno, iz svoje perspektive,

755
00:38:46,699 --> 00:38:47,599
[SPEAKER_00] sad sam objasnio,

756
00:38:47,599 --> 00:38:49,699
[SPEAKER_00] recimo,

757
00:38:49,699 --> 00:38:53,860
[SPEAKER_00] u Africi nemaju problema sa ovim Isusova braća i sestre.

758
00:38:53,860 --> 00:38:54,980
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nemaju problema.

759
00:38:54,980 --> 00:38:58,260
[SPEAKER_00] Znaju da to može biti puno širi pojam od nuklearne obitelji.

760
00:38:58,260 --> 00:38:59,780
[SPEAKER_00] Mi u Evropi imamo,

761
00:38:59,780 --> 00:39:02,159
[SPEAKER_00] to je bio jedan kamel s poticanja, jel?

762
00:39:02,159 --> 00:39:02,920
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

763
00:39:02,920 --> 00:39:06,340
[SPEAKER_00] i, naravno, pogani koji ne razumije uopće

764
00:39:06,340 --> 00:39:07,800
[SPEAKER_00] niti židovsku terminologiju

765
00:39:07,800 --> 00:39:10,059
[SPEAKER_00] i tako, onda lagano dobivamo

766
00:39:10,059 --> 00:39:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] apokrife o starcu Josipu

767
00:39:13,000 --> 00:39:14,820
[SPEAKER_00] i o udovcu Josipu.

768
00:39:14,820 --> 00:39:16,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću vam pročitati

769
00:39:16,340 --> 00:39:17,699
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo zanimljivu priču,

770
00:39:17,699 --> 00:39:18,500
[SPEAKER_00] jedan apokrif,

771
00:39:18,500 --> 00:39:21,099
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, čisto da znate od kuda uopće potiče

772
00:39:21,099 --> 00:39:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] takva slika svetoga Josipa

773
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:23,960
[SPEAKER_00] kao jednome starcu,

774
00:39:23,960 --> 00:39:25,320
[SPEAKER_00] a onda ćemo, naravno,

775
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] ono što je zanimljivo,

776
00:39:26,420 --> 00:39:28,280
[SPEAKER_00] za koji trenutak doći do,

777
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:30,340
[SPEAKER_00] idemo izračunati koliko je zapravo Josip

778
00:39:30,340 --> 00:39:31,920
[SPEAKER_00] fakat imao godina.

779
00:39:32,679 --> 00:39:34,179
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, prije svega,

780
00:39:34,179 --> 00:39:35,820
[SPEAKER_00] možete ovo maknuti,

781
00:39:35,820 --> 00:39:37,099
[SPEAKER_00] ovo vam jasno,

782
00:39:37,099 --> 00:39:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] jasno, jel?

783
00:39:37,619 --> 00:39:38,860
[SPEAKER_00] Vrlo jednostavno, pa da,

784
00:39:38,860 --> 00:39:40,179
[SPEAKER_00] ok, dobro,

785
00:39:40,179 --> 00:39:40,980
[SPEAKER_00] ako sam ja skužio,

786
00:39:40,980 --> 00:39:42,099
[SPEAKER_00] ćete fakt ti skužiti.

787
00:39:42,099 --> 00:39:43,239
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro,

788
00:39:43,239 --> 00:39:45,039
[SPEAKER_00] pročitaću,

789
00:39:45,039 --> 00:39:45,559
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

790
00:39:45,559 --> 00:39:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] jako je dugačak,

791
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:49,099
[SPEAKER_00] pa ću ja ovako više

792
00:39:49,099 --> 00:39:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] prepričat možda u tom smislu,

793
00:39:51,659 --> 00:39:53,119
[SPEAKER_00] da to sad ne traje.

794
00:39:53,119 --> 00:39:54,260
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

795
00:39:54,260 --> 00:39:56,860
[SPEAKER_00] jako je ovoproto evanđelje,

796
00:39:56,860 --> 00:39:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

797
00:39:57,159 --> 00:39:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] to je apokrif,

798
00:39:58,539 --> 00:39:59,760
[SPEAKER_00] znate što su apokrifi,

799
00:39:59,760 --> 00:40:00,679
[SPEAKER_00] imali smo čak i

800
00:40:00,679 --> 00:40:02,400
[SPEAKER_00] ciklus kateheza o apokrifima,

801
00:40:02,400 --> 00:40:03,219
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

802
00:40:03,219 --> 00:40:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] apokrif,

803
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

804
00:40:04,420 --> 00:40:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] ono što je skriveno,

805
00:40:05,539 --> 00:40:06,239
[SPEAKER_00] skrivena knjiga,

806
00:40:06,239 --> 00:40:06,579
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

807
00:40:06,579 --> 00:40:08,619
[SPEAKER_00] to su evanđelja iz pisi,

808
00:40:08,619 --> 00:40:09,400
[SPEAKER_00] koji,

809
00:40:09,400 --> 00:40:10,800
[SPEAKER_00] kad su pisani,

810
00:40:10,800 --> 00:40:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] pisi su htjeli

811
00:40:12,539 --> 00:40:13,699
[SPEAKER_00] da imaju status

812
00:40:13,699 --> 00:40:14,900
[SPEAKER_00] kanonskog evanđelja,

813
00:40:14,900 --> 00:40:15,199
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

814
00:40:15,199 --> 00:40:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] da imaju tu snagu

815
00:40:16,519 --> 00:40:17,320
[SPEAKER_00] kao što imaju

816
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:18,800
[SPEAKER_00] Mate, Marko, Luka i tako dalje.

817
00:40:18,800 --> 00:40:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da,

818
00:40:20,440 --> 00:40:22,260
[SPEAKER_00] pravi pisi nisu

819
00:40:22,260 --> 00:40:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] niti Jakov,

820
00:40:23,039 --> 00:40:23,679
[SPEAKER_00] niti Juda,

821
00:40:23,679 --> 00:40:24,639
[SPEAKER_00] niti Petar,

822
00:40:24,639 --> 00:40:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] niti, ne znam koja više sve nije,

823
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:26,840
[SPEAKER_00] Marija Magdalena,

824
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:28,719
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam koja više nema svoje evanđelje,

825
00:40:28,719 --> 00:40:31,440
[SPEAKER_00] nego onaj koji je htio prodati svoju,

826
00:40:31,440 --> 00:40:32,139
[SPEAKER_00] znači, ovako,

827
00:40:32,139 --> 00:40:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] evanđelja koja je u evanđeljima,

828
00:40:34,920 --> 00:40:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] jel?

829
00:40:35,159 --> 00:40:35,699
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

830
00:40:35,699 --> 00:40:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] to su evanđelje iz prvog stoljeća,

831
00:40:37,920 --> 00:40:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] neposredna svjedočanstva,

832
00:40:39,380 --> 00:40:39,719
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

833
00:40:39,719 --> 00:40:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] i oni koji su to,

834
00:40:40,619 --> 00:40:41,820
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

835
00:40:41,820 --> 00:40:42,400
[SPEAKER_00] pisali,

836
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:43,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan i Matej,

837
00:40:43,440 --> 00:40:44,960
[SPEAKER_00] su bili neposredni svjedoci,

838
00:40:44,960 --> 00:40:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] a Marko i Luka su bili,

839
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:51,219
[SPEAKER_00] svjedoci u smislu da su slušali od apostola,

840
00:40:51,219 --> 00:40:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] nekog od apostola,

841
00:40:51,980 --> 00:40:52,519
[SPEAKER_00] od Pavla,

842
00:40:52,519 --> 00:40:53,679
[SPEAKER_00] a ovo je od Petra.

843
00:40:53,679 --> 00:40:55,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ova ostala,

844
00:40:55,280 --> 00:40:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

845
00:40:56,119 --> 00:40:58,800
[SPEAKER_00] čim je evanđelje iz trećeg stoljeća,

846
00:40:58,800 --> 00:41:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] tu da počinu ja po krifi,

847
00:41:00,059 --> 00:41:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] kasnije drugo stoljeće,

848
00:41:02,519 --> 00:41:03,659
[SPEAKER_00] trećeg stoljeća,

849
00:41:03,659 --> 00:41:05,980
[SPEAKER_00] sve do osmog, devetog stoljeća,

850
00:41:05,980 --> 00:41:06,760
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

851
00:41:06,760 --> 00:41:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] ne možemo govoriti o autentičnim svjedočanstvima,

852
00:41:10,159 --> 00:41:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] zašto su se pisala?

853
00:41:11,119 --> 00:41:11,760
[SPEAKER_00] Zato,

854
00:41:11,760 --> 00:41:12,039
[SPEAKER_00] odako,

855
00:41:12,039 --> 00:41:14,300
[SPEAKER_00] da hrane,

856
00:41:14,300 --> 00:41:15,119
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo reći,

857
00:41:15,119 --> 00:41:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] pučku znati želju,

858
00:41:16,500 --> 00:41:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] pučku znati želju,

859
00:41:17,619 --> 00:41:17,860
[SPEAKER_00] kako,

860
00:41:17,860 --> 00:41:18,219
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

861
00:41:18,219 --> 00:41:20,119
[SPEAKER_00] čemu se najčešće pisalo?

862
00:41:20,119 --> 00:41:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] O Isusovom djetinstvu,

863
00:41:21,400 --> 00:41:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] jer jako malo imamo ti detalje o Isusovom djetinstvu,

864
00:41:23,460 --> 00:41:24,340
[SPEAKER_00] u ovim evanđeljima,

865
00:41:24,340 --> 00:41:24,820
[SPEAKER_00] je li tako?

866
00:41:24,820 --> 00:41:25,639
[SPEAKER_00] I naravno,

867
00:41:25,639 --> 00:41:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] potpisivali su se kao neki od apostola,

868
00:41:28,039 --> 00:41:29,900
[SPEAKER_00] jer ako želiš prodati svoju priču,

869
00:41:29,900 --> 00:41:30,519
[SPEAKER_00] svoju knjigu,

870
00:41:30,519 --> 00:41:33,800
[SPEAKER_00] on se potpiši kao neki autoritet crkveni,

871
00:41:33,800 --> 00:41:34,320
[SPEAKER_00] koji tada,

872
00:41:34,320 --> 00:41:35,300
[SPEAKER_00] itekako imao,

873
00:41:35,519 --> 00:41:36,400
[SPEAKER_00] itekako imao snagu.

874
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:36,719
[SPEAKER_00] To što,

875
00:41:36,719 --> 00:41:38,800
[SPEAKER_00] ako ću ja napisat neko evanđelje,

