1092
00:46:37,679 --> 00:46:38,719
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro,

1093
00:46:38,719 --> 00:46:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] ok.

1094
00:46:39,079 --> 00:46:41,739
[SPEAKER_00] Da,

1095
00:46:41,739 --> 00:46:42,920
[SPEAKER_00] i kasnije se opisuje,

1096
00:46:42,920 --> 00:46:43,739
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

1097
00:46:43,739 --> 00:46:45,780
[SPEAKER_00] da Josip tada ima 80 godina,

1098
00:46:45,780 --> 00:46:47,500
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

1099
00:46:47,500 --> 00:46:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] da je,

1100
00:46:48,199 --> 00:46:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj,

1101
00:46:48,940 --> 00:46:52,480
[SPEAKER_00] počeo umirati sa 90 godina,

1102
00:46:52,480 --> 00:46:54,659
[SPEAKER_00] a da je napokon umro sa 120 godina.

1103
00:46:54,659 --> 00:46:55,079
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

1104
00:46:55,079 --> 00:46:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] to isto,

1105
00:46:55,500 --> 00:46:58,280
[SPEAKER_00] proto evanđelje to tako opisuje.

1106
00:46:58,280 --> 00:46:59,519
[SPEAKER_00] A bez da je onda dživio Isusa.

1107
00:46:59,519 --> 00:47:01,239
[SPEAKER_00] Sve,

1108
00:47:01,239 --> 00:47:02,280
[SPEAKER_00] i Mariju i sve.

1109
00:47:02,500 --> 00:47:02,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro,

1110
00:47:02,800 --> 00:47:03,139
[SPEAKER_00] ok.

1111
00:47:03,139 --> 00:47:04,880
[SPEAKER_00] E sada,

1112
00:47:04,880 --> 00:47:05,340
[SPEAKER_00] idemo

1113
00:47:05,340 --> 00:47:07,639
[SPEAKER_00] prema zaključcima.

1114
00:47:07,639 --> 00:47:10,280
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo vidjeti

1115
00:47:10,280 --> 00:47:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] kako nam evanđelja,

1116
00:47:11,380 --> 00:47:11,840
[SPEAKER_00] to ću mi,

1117
00:47:11,840 --> 00:47:12,139
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj,

1118
00:47:12,139 --> 00:47:12,960
[SPEAKER_00] sam fakat jelom,

1119
00:47:12,960 --> 00:47:13,780
[SPEAKER_00] grčki,

1120
00:47:13,780 --> 00:47:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] latinski novi zavijet.

1121
00:47:15,039 --> 00:47:17,260
[SPEAKER_00] Želite malo čuti grčko,

1122
00:47:17,260 --> 00:47:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] onako,

1123
00:47:17,559 --> 00:47:18,239
[SPEAKER_00] čisto malo,

1124
00:47:18,239 --> 00:47:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] onako,

1125
00:47:18,559 --> 00:47:19,300
[SPEAKER_00] može,

1126
00:47:19,300 --> 00:47:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] može,

1127
00:47:19,599 --> 00:47:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] ok.

1128
00:47:19,880 --> 00:47:21,619
[SPEAKER_00] Pa čisto veće vrijeme za spavanje,

1129
00:47:21,619 --> 00:47:22,719
[SPEAKER_00] pa da vas još više uspava.

1130
00:47:22,719 --> 00:47:23,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ali,

1131
00:47:23,440 --> 00:47:23,840
[SPEAKER_00] ovo,

1132
00:47:23,840 --> 00:47:25,659
[SPEAKER_00] nije samo stvar toga da ga čujete,

1133
00:47:25,659 --> 00:47:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] nego da vidite kako će nam pomoći

1134
00:47:27,880 --> 00:47:30,440
[SPEAKER_00] da vidimo koliko Josip imao godina.

1135
00:47:30,440 --> 00:47:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

1136
00:47:31,239 --> 00:47:32,679
[SPEAKER_00] kada se dogodilo navištaje,

1137
00:47:32,679 --> 00:47:33,719
[SPEAKER_00] kada se dogodilo sve ovo,

1138
00:47:33,719 --> 00:47:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] anđeo u snu i tako dalje,

1139
00:47:35,079 --> 00:47:36,679
[SPEAKER_00] kada ga uopće upoznajemo,

1140
00:47:36,679 --> 00:47:38,480
[SPEAKER_00] kada ga prvi put se sretimo s Josipom,

1141
00:47:38,480 --> 00:47:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] koliko on tada ima godina.

1142
00:47:40,460 --> 00:47:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je zapravo jako mi pomoglo,

1143
00:47:43,059 --> 00:47:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] prije svega,

1144
00:47:44,920 --> 00:47:46,880
[SPEAKER_00] kada Luka opisuje,

1145
00:47:46,880 --> 00:47:47,860
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo reći,

1146
00:47:47,860 --> 00:47:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] dva muškarca,

1147
00:47:48,860 --> 00:47:51,280
[SPEAKER_00] kojima se događa navištenje.

1148
00:47:51,280 --> 00:47:52,360
[SPEAKER_00] Prvi je Zaharija,

1149
00:47:52,360 --> 00:47:52,940
[SPEAKER_00] je li tako,

1150
00:47:52,940 --> 00:47:55,639
[SPEAKER_00] navištenje rođenja Ivana Krstitelja,

1151
00:47:55,639 --> 00:47:58,360
[SPEAKER_00] i drugi je Josip.

1152
00:47:58,760 --> 00:48:02,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte kako Luka 1.18 kaže ovdje za Zahariju.

1153
00:48:02,199 --> 00:48:05,239
[SPEAKER_00] Dato Zaharija reče Anđelu,

1154
00:48:05,239 --> 00:48:07,260
[SPEAKER_00] po čemu ću ja to razaznati?

1155
00:48:07,260 --> 00:48:08,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ta star sam,

1156
00:48:08,260 --> 00:48:09,360
[SPEAKER_00] prezbites,

1157
00:48:09,360 --> 00:48:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] i žena mi je podmakle dobi.

1158
00:48:12,519 --> 00:48:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] Luka 1.26.27 kaže ovo,

1159
00:48:15,900 --> 00:48:18,739
[SPEAKER_00] u šestove mjesecu posla bog Anđela Gabrijela,

1160
00:48:18,739 --> 00:48:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] u Galilejski grad imenom Nazaret,

1161
00:48:20,440 --> 00:48:23,739
[SPEAKER_00] gdjevići zaručenoj s mužem Aner,

1162
00:48:23,739 --> 00:48:24,420
[SPEAKER_00] grčki,

1163
00:48:24,420 --> 00:48:26,119
[SPEAKER_00] dakle Zaharija je prezbites,

1164
00:48:26,119 --> 00:48:28,840
[SPEAKER_00] a Josip je Aner,

1165
00:48:28,840 --> 00:48:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] muž mladić.

1166
00:48:30,559 --> 00:48:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] Sad sam spojilo.

1167
00:48:32,039 --> 00:48:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali dobro, ne znam te koliko ima godina.

1168
00:48:33,539 --> 00:48:34,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ok,

1169
00:48:34,300 --> 00:48:38,019
[SPEAKER_00] koji se zvao Josip iz doma Davidova?

1170
00:48:38,019 --> 00:48:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

1171
00:48:38,960 --> 00:48:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] tako i ovdje kaže,

1172
00:48:40,960 --> 00:48:42,300
[SPEAKER_00] znači prvo za Zahariju,

1173
00:48:42,300 --> 00:48:44,820
[SPEAKER_00] kaj eipen zakarijas proston agelon,

1174
00:48:44,820 --> 00:48:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] katati ignosoma ituto ego gar emi prezbites,

1175
00:48:48,840 --> 00:48:50,099
[SPEAKER_00] dakle starat sam,

1176
00:48:50,099 --> 00:48:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] star sam čovjek.

1177
00:48:51,079 --> 00:48:52,300
[SPEAKER_00] Dok isti,

1178
00:48:52,300 --> 00:48:53,019
[SPEAKER_00] dakle Luka,

1179
00:48:53,019 --> 00:48:54,079
[SPEAKER_00] kaže za,

1180
00:48:54,079 --> 00:48:56,480
[SPEAKER_00] Luka ovo može najbolje znati u grčkom,

1181
00:48:56,480 --> 00:48:58,179
[SPEAKER_00] jer on je jedini od evanđelista,

1182
00:48:58,179 --> 00:48:59,179
[SPEAKER_00] izvodni govornik,

1183
00:48:59,179 --> 00:49:00,840
[SPEAKER_00] izvodni govornik grčkog jezika.

1184
00:49:00,840 --> 00:49:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] On piše na svom materijskom jeziku,

1185
00:49:02,539 --> 00:49:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] na grčkom.

1186
00:49:03,079 --> 00:49:04,360
[SPEAKER_00] Znavo da Matej,

1187
00:49:04,360 --> 00:49:07,739
[SPEAKER_00] Marko i Ivan su židovi koji,

1188
00:49:07,739 --> 00:49:10,019
[SPEAKER_00] naravno njihov materijski aramejski,

1189
00:49:10,059 --> 00:49:11,280
[SPEAKER_00] oni pišu na grčkom,

1190
00:49:11,280 --> 00:49:12,340
[SPEAKER_00] tako da Luka nam je ovdje

1191
00:49:12,340 --> 00:49:14,159
[SPEAKER_00] najautentičniji u tom smislu.

1192
00:49:14,159 --> 00:49:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, prezbite za Zahariju

1193
00:49:16,440 --> 00:49:20,340
[SPEAKER_00] i tako ovdje kaže za Josipa,

1194
00:49:20,340 --> 00:49:21,699
[SPEAKER_00] pros Partenon,

1195
00:49:21,699 --> 00:49:22,800
[SPEAKER_00] Partenon je djevica,

1196
00:49:22,800 --> 00:49:24,639
[SPEAKER_00] emneste women,

1197
00:49:24,639 --> 00:49:25,280
[SPEAKER_00] Andri,

1198
00:49:25,280 --> 00:49:27,059
[SPEAKER_00] Andri je dativ od Aner,

1199
00:49:27,059 --> 00:49:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

1200
00:49:27,639 --> 00:49:30,519
[SPEAKER_00] hoonoma Josep,

1201
00:49:30,519 --> 00:49:31,619
[SPEAKER_00] koji se zvao Josip.

1202
00:49:31,619 --> 00:49:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] E sad gledajte ovo,

1203
00:49:32,480 --> 00:49:34,739
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, prezbites i Aner.

1204
00:49:34,739 --> 00:49:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo vidjeti koja je bila Josipova dob.

1205
00:49:37,920 --> 00:49:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] Filon Aleksandrijski,

1206
00:49:39,880 --> 00:49:44,139
[SPEAKER_00] koji je isto židov koji piše na grčkom,

1207
00:49:44,139 --> 00:49:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] u svojom spisu o stvaranju svijeta,

1208
00:49:46,820 --> 00:49:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] 105. glava,

1209
00:49:48,860 --> 00:49:51,960
[SPEAKER_00] ovako opisuje muškarčevu dob.

1210
00:49:54,159 --> 00:49:56,079
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to je, on je isto iz prvog stoljeća.

1211
00:49:56,079 --> 00:49:57,900
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je židov isto iz prvog stoljeća.

1212
00:49:57,900 --> 00:50:01,679
[SPEAKER_00] Dječak je, dok mu brada ne počne rasti.

1213
00:50:01,679 --> 00:50:05,099
[SPEAKER_00] I dječačko doba traje do trećeg razdoblja od sedam godina.

1214
00:50:05,840 --> 00:50:08,920
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatski je rečeno, dok ne napuni 21. godinu.

1215
00:50:08,920 --> 00:50:10,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, dok ne napuni 21. godinu.

1216
00:50:11,559 --> 00:50:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] Mladić je neadiskos, grčki se kaže neadiskos za mladića,

1217
00:50:15,559 --> 00:50:18,480
[SPEAKER_00] do potpunog zazrijevanja cijeloga tijela,

1218
00:50:18,480 --> 00:50:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] što se slaže sa četvrtim periodom od sedam godina.

1219
00:50:21,340 --> 00:50:23,079
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, dok ne napuni 28 godina.

1220
00:50:23,500 --> 00:50:26,820
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, od 21 do 28 si neadiskos, mladić.

1221
00:50:26,820 --> 00:50:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je muž, muž njezin pravedan.

1222
00:50:31,000 --> 00:50:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Muž, a ner, dakle, od 28, dok ne napuni 40 godina.

1223
00:50:38,000 --> 00:50:43,900
[SPEAKER_00] Zreliji je čovjek, prezbites, odnosno stariji čovjek, krivo, prezbites,

1224
00:50:43,900 --> 00:50:47,840
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ovo što se za Zahariju kaže, dok ne napuni 56 godina.

1225
00:50:47,840 --> 00:50:49,179
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga je starac.

1226
00:50:49,179 --> 00:50:51,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ima neko više od 56 godina.

1227
00:50:53,500 --> 00:50:58,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, mi vidimo, dakle, i ovdje Luka je stavio,

1228
00:50:58,860 --> 00:51:02,199
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, kad ima izričaj, a ner, dakle, a ner,

1229
00:51:02,199 --> 00:51:10,360
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, je izričaj za muškarca koji ima od 28 do 40 godina.

1230
00:51:10,360 --> 00:51:15,719
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Josip je bio u punoj snazi, možemo to tako reći,

1231
00:51:15,719 --> 00:51:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] nije bio nikakav starac, znači je bio ili u kasnim 20-tima,

1232
00:51:18,920 --> 00:51:20,760
[SPEAKER_00] ili u svojim 30-tima.

1233
00:51:20,760 --> 00:51:22,079
[SPEAKER_00] I to je vrlo važno.

1234
00:51:22,440 --> 00:51:25,239
[SPEAKER_00] Nije čak ni dobro da je onako neani skos mladić, jel?

1235
00:51:25,239 --> 00:51:28,860
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što je balavac, koga može ozbiljno shvatiti.

1236
00:51:28,860 --> 00:51:31,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovo je zapravo najbolje da ti bude hranitelj, jel tako?

1237
00:51:31,920 --> 00:51:35,139
[SPEAKER_00] Mlade obitelji, znači, miša nemoj se uvrijediti.

1238
00:51:35,139 --> 00:51:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ali evo, jebanđelja nam sama, sama kažu,

1239
00:51:39,940 --> 00:51:45,219
[SPEAKER_00] period u kojem je Josip mogao biti star.

1240
00:51:45,219 --> 00:51:46,940
[SPEAKER_00] Od 28 do 40.

1241
00:51:47,139 --> 00:51:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] Aner, muž.

1242
00:51:47,980 --> 00:51:49,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, dobro.

1243
00:51:49,679 --> 00:51:53,519
[SPEAKER_00] E sada zadnje pitanje, zaključno pitanje koje jest ovdje.

1244
00:51:53,519 --> 00:51:58,940
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, jesu li onda Josip i Marija bili u braku u pravu smislu riječi?

1245
00:51:58,940 --> 00:52:04,900
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što opet mi europski, malo možda i svjetovno razmišljamo da nije brak dok se ne kozumira.

1246
00:52:05,059 --> 00:52:10,179
[SPEAKER_00] Čak i ako se na kraju uspostavi da je par možda neplodana, ali ono, bar su probali,

1247
00:52:10,179 --> 00:52:11,519
[SPEAKER_00] konzumirali su, je li tako?

1248
00:52:11,519 --> 00:52:13,320
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je to brak u pravu smislu riječi.

1249
00:52:13,320 --> 00:52:21,139
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, evo, Tom Akvinski u teološkoj sumi 3.29.2 kaže,

1250
00:52:21,139 --> 00:52:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] Čije se kao da nije bilo pravoga braka između Josipa i Marije.

1251
00:52:25,019 --> 00:52:32,099
[SPEAKER_00] Naprotiv, Augustin kaže, ako su nakon sklapanja braka ostali postojani uzajavnim pristakom na uzdržavanje,

1252
00:52:32,099 --> 00:52:36,280
[SPEAKER_00] ono što su pročitali iz knjige Brojeva, njihov savez je i nadalje brak.

1253
00:52:36,280 --> 00:52:42,079
[SPEAKER_00] Forma ženitbe sadrži nerazdvojeno sjedinjenje duša, po čemu muži žena priste u jedno uz drugo

1254
00:52:42,079 --> 00:52:45,739
[SPEAKER_00] uzajavnim privlačenjem koje se ne može omalovažiti.

1255
00:52:45,739 --> 00:52:48,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću ovo sad malo spustiti na našu razinu.

1256
00:52:48,639 --> 00:52:49,980
[SPEAKER_00] Što je ovdje Toma htio reći?

1257
00:52:49,980 --> 00:52:56,159
[SPEAKER_00] A ono što i u Redemptoris Custos, da, Ivan Pavel II, o svetome Josipu,

1258
00:52:56,159 --> 00:53:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, isto slično kaže, već je kasno pa ga neću previše citirati,

1259
00:53:00,239 --> 00:53:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] ali jedno i drugo zapravo želi reći ovo.

1260
00:53:02,519 --> 00:53:08,980
[SPEAKER_00] Uzajavni, kad gledate isklapanje vlastitoga braka, zapravo morate gledati iz te perspektive.

1261
00:53:08,980 --> 00:53:13,880
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, uzajavni pristanak, a ne kozumacija, čini brak.

1262
00:53:13,880 --> 00:53:15,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ok?

1263
00:53:15,139 --> 00:53:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, sjedinjenje duša prije nego sjedinjenje tijela.

1264
00:53:19,219 --> 00:53:22,980
[SPEAKER_00] Kada vi ovdje, dakle, jednom i drugome date uzajavni pristanak,

1265
00:53:22,980 --> 00:53:29,179
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, dajete braše zavijete na dan svoga vječanja i sada ne stignete ga konzumirati,

1266
00:53:29,179 --> 00:53:33,480
[SPEAKER_00] jer na odlasku van muža je strefil infarkt i on je umro,

1267
00:53:33,480 --> 00:53:36,179
[SPEAKER_00] njegova mlada je udovica.

1268
00:53:36,179 --> 00:53:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] Jel' tako? Njegova mlada je udovica.

1269
00:53:38,659 --> 00:53:39,579
[SPEAKER_00] On su sklopili brak.

1270
00:53:39,579 --> 00:53:42,280
[SPEAKER_00] Na vezi ga još nisu otišli u krevet i lamedjeni mjesec.

1271
00:53:42,619 --> 00:53:43,099
[SPEAKER_00] Razumijete?

1272
00:53:43,099 --> 00:53:45,400
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovo se želi ovdje reći.

1273
00:53:45,400 --> 00:53:46,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj, dakle, što?

1274
00:53:46,800 --> 00:53:49,219
[SPEAKER_00] Što nju nju nju treba.

1275
00:53:49,219 --> 00:53:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne znam, možda muškima teže padne.

1276
00:53:52,699 --> 00:53:55,920
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1277
00:53:55,920 --> 00:53:59,820
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, isto kažemo, oni su u braku.

1278
00:53:59,820 --> 00:54:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tu, istu se, i kaže, vi ste sada muž i žena.

1279
00:54:02,960 --> 00:54:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] Na sam da, ne kaže, nije svećenik da ono, ne kaže, vi ste sada muž i žena.

1280
00:54:06,980 --> 00:54:09,980
[SPEAKER_00] Čeka ono, kad mu jave, evo, bavili smo ono što smo trebali,

1281
00:54:09,980 --> 00:54:13,619
[SPEAKER_00] i onda sad kaže, ehe, nas vas zvona, oni su sad muž i ženi, jer su sad konzumirali brak.

1282
00:54:13,619 --> 00:54:14,059
[SPEAKER_00] Jel tako?

1283
00:54:14,059 --> 00:54:18,739
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, uzajamni pristanak je brak, a ne konzumacija.

1284
00:54:18,739 --> 00:54:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] To je vrlo važno.

1285
00:54:20,159 --> 00:54:24,840
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ono, kad gledate zakonji kauskog prava, kaže da je koja je uloga ženitbe,

1286
00:54:24,840 --> 00:54:28,360
[SPEAKER_00] broj jedan nije rađanje odgajanje potomstva,

1287
00:54:28,360 --> 00:54:34,139
[SPEAKER_00] nego, dakle, broj jedan je uzajamna, ajmo reći, uzajamna korist,

1288
00:54:34,139 --> 00:54:36,260
[SPEAKER_00] poštivanje ljubav, bračnih drugova.

1289
00:54:36,260 --> 00:54:40,719
[SPEAKER_00] A onda, nakon toga, dolazi, dakle, rađanje odgajanje potomstva.

1290
00:54:40,719 --> 00:54:44,820
[SPEAKER_00] Jer po tome, onda, oni koji ne mogu začeti, ili su neplodni,

1291
00:54:44,820 --> 00:54:48,519
[SPEAKER_00] što onda možemo reći da žive pravi brak, nemaju pravo obite, jel?

1292
00:54:48,519 --> 00:54:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1293
00:54:49,559 --> 00:54:54,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, e, i sada zadnja stvar, evo, ovo je sada definitivno zadnja stvar,

1294
00:54:54,800 --> 00:54:56,900
[SPEAKER_00] a vjerujem da ćemo biti zadimljivija od ovoga,

1295
00:54:56,900 --> 00:55:02,699
[SPEAKER_00] a to je kako je Josip sakrio djevičansko porođenje od Satone.

1296
00:55:02,699 --> 00:55:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što sam malo na početku isto najavio.

1297
00:55:05,960 --> 00:55:08,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, zašto je to važno?

1298
00:55:08,760 --> 00:55:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] Uopće znati, ja imam to tako reći.

1299
00:55:11,599 --> 00:55:16,300
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, uopće to vidite koje je značaj djevičanskog začeća.

1300
00:55:16,300 --> 00:55:19,179
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što se isto postavlja pitanje, pa dobro,

1301
00:55:19,179 --> 00:55:22,739
[SPEAKER_00] ako je Bog htio već djevičansko začeće, jel tako,

1302
00:55:22,739 --> 00:55:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] pa zašto je otišao udanoj ženi?

1303
00:55:24,500 --> 00:55:27,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Marija je udana žena u trenutku navještelja, to smo dokazali.

1304
00:55:27,420 --> 00:55:31,219
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je otišao nekoj tamo koji još nema niti muža,

1305
00:55:31,219 --> 00:55:35,300
[SPEAKER_00] niti ono, nikoga ni u primisle, zašto je došao udanoj ženi?

1306
00:55:35,300 --> 00:55:36,960
[SPEAKER_00] Nije fair, zašto?

1307
00:55:36,960 --> 00:55:37,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ali tako?

1308
00:55:37,739 --> 00:55:40,480
[SPEAKER_00] Gledajte kako Origen u svojim homilijama,

1309
00:55:40,480 --> 00:55:42,320
[SPEAKER_00] ali i katekizam katoličke crkve,

1310
00:55:42,320 --> 00:55:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] da ne bi neki teolozi koji slušaju

1311
00:55:44,539 --> 00:55:47,659
[SPEAKER_00] kaj se sad našao Origena, on nijediti svet,

1312
00:55:47,659 --> 00:55:52,559
[SPEAKER_00] on je heretik i tako, nije heretik, nije, samo je krivo obdužen,

1313
00:55:52,739 --> 00:55:53,519
[SPEAKER_00] ali dobro, ok.

1314
00:55:53,519 --> 00:55:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] U svojim homilijama najevađenje po Luki kaže ovo, 6, 3 do 5.

1315
00:55:57,539 --> 00:56:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je Bog, kada je odlučio da spasitelj bude rođen od djevice,

1316
00:56:02,019 --> 00:56:04,820
[SPEAKER_00] bira upravo onu zaručenu, čite udanu,

1317
00:56:04,820 --> 00:56:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] a ne onu koja nije zaručena?

1318
00:56:07,199 --> 00:56:11,199
[SPEAKER_00] Naišao sam na prekrasnu misao u pismu mučenika Ignace,

1319
00:56:11,199 --> 00:56:12,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ignace Antiohijskoj.

1320
00:56:12,300 --> 00:56:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže,

1321
00:56:12,940 --> 00:56:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] Marijino djevičanstvo je promaklo pažnji vladaru ovoga vremena,

1322
00:56:17,340 --> 00:56:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] satona, jel?

1323
00:56:18,019 --> 00:56:20,679
[SPEAKER_00] Promaklo je upravo zahvaljujući Josipu

1324
00:56:20,679 --> 00:56:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] i zbog njihova vjenčanja,

1325
00:56:22,420 --> 00:56:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] jer se smatralo da Marija ima muža.

1326
00:56:24,880 --> 00:56:26,519
[SPEAKER_00] Da nije bila zaručena,

1327
00:56:26,519 --> 00:56:29,179
[SPEAKER_00] ili da nije imala, kako su mislili ljudi, muža,

1328
00:56:29,179 --> 00:56:31,880
[SPEAKER_00] njeno djevičanstvo se nikako ne bi moglo sakriti

1329
00:56:31,880 --> 00:56:33,179
[SPEAKER_00] od knjeza ovoga svijeta.

1330
00:56:33,179 --> 00:56:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ubah tiha misao bi se rodila u džavlu.

1331
00:56:36,139 --> 00:56:37,860
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ova žena može biti trudna?

1332
00:56:37,860 --> 00:56:40,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo začeće mora biti božansko,

1333
00:56:40,019 --> 00:56:41,800
[SPEAKER_00] mora biti izvan ljudske moći,

1334
00:56:41,800 --> 00:56:43,820
[SPEAKER_00] ali je spasitelj sve tako uredio

1335
00:56:43,820 --> 00:56:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] da džavao nije ni znao

1336
00:56:45,619 --> 00:56:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] da je Bog već uzeo ljudsko tijelo.

1337
00:56:48,300 --> 00:56:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Josipe, strahu zlih duhova, je li tako?

1338
00:56:51,199 --> 00:56:53,260
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ono što će reći ovdje

1339
00:56:53,260 --> 00:56:55,400
[SPEAKER_00] i katekizam katoličke crkve,

1340
00:56:55,400 --> 00:56:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] razumijete ovo.

1341
00:56:56,500 --> 00:56:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, dok je trajalo

1342
00:56:59,039 --> 00:57:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] ostvarenje,

1343
00:57:00,940 --> 00:57:03,239
[SPEAKER_00] dok je u tijeku bio proces

1344
00:57:03,239 --> 00:57:05,639
[SPEAKER_00] ostvarivanja božjega plana spasenja,

1345
00:57:05,639 --> 00:57:07,900
[SPEAKER_00] sve je moralo biti

1346
00:57:07,900 --> 00:57:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] besprijekono i tajnovito.

1347
00:57:09,420 --> 00:57:10,519
[SPEAKER_00] Razumijete?

1348
00:57:10,639 --> 00:57:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] Zato Bog nije,

1349
00:57:12,159 --> 00:57:13,760
[SPEAKER_00] Isus nimao problema s time,

1350
00:57:13,760 --> 00:57:16,099
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, možda ni danas

1351
00:57:16,099 --> 00:57:17,480
[SPEAKER_00] da se smatra da imao baš ono,

1352
00:57:17,480 --> 00:57:18,880
[SPEAKER_00] braču, sestri i tako dalje.

1353
00:57:18,880 --> 00:57:21,719
[SPEAKER_00] I nisu imali problema s time

1354
00:57:21,719 --> 00:57:22,760
[SPEAKER_00] da su ljudi možda mislili,

1355
00:57:22,760 --> 00:57:23,940
[SPEAKER_00] ko zna šta Marija i Josip rade

1356
00:57:23,940 --> 00:57:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] u tom svom braku,

1357
00:57:24,599 --> 00:57:25,940
[SPEAKER_00] bažnji već istoću može se misliti.

1358
00:57:26,039 --> 00:57:30,260
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što se htijelo sakrit

1359
00:57:30,260 --> 00:57:32,940
[SPEAKER_00] upravo to njezino djevičanstvo

1360
00:57:32,940 --> 00:57:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] i djevičansko začeće.

1361
00:57:35,119 --> 00:57:36,760
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je, odavne, naravno.

1362
00:57:36,760 --> 00:57:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je Sotoni to promaklo,

1363
00:57:39,500 --> 00:57:40,480
[SPEAKER_00] upravo zbog Josipa,

1364
00:57:40,480 --> 00:57:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] koji je uzeo Mariju.

1365
00:57:42,460 --> 00:57:43,900
[SPEAKER_00] Jer on nije gledao,

1366
00:57:43,900 --> 00:57:46,400
[SPEAKER_00] znači, on je gledao djevice.

1367
00:57:46,400 --> 00:57:49,280
[SPEAKER_00] Gledao je djevičansko začeće,

1368
00:57:49,280 --> 00:57:52,360
[SPEAKER_00] moglo bi Bogu upast šefu tamo gore na pamet,

1369
00:57:52,360 --> 00:57:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] je li tako, tako nešto.

1370
00:57:53,539 --> 00:57:55,219
[SPEAKER_00] I naravno da je gledao takve.

1371
00:57:56,039 --> 00:57:57,780
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, gledati nekoga ko je već u braku.

1372
00:57:57,780 --> 00:57:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] Nije ga zadimalo.

1373
00:57:58,880 --> 00:58:00,159
[SPEAKER_00] Je li tako, on je već u braku.

1374
00:58:00,159 --> 00:58:02,699
[SPEAKER_00] Sigurno je kozumirao brak itd.

1375
00:58:02,699 --> 00:58:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] I tome slično.

1376
00:58:03,840 --> 00:58:05,599
[SPEAKER_00] I zato, razumijete ovo,

1377
00:58:05,599 --> 00:58:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, i zato kada Isusu sreće

1378
00:58:09,000 --> 00:58:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] Sotonu ili demone,

1379
00:58:11,059 --> 00:58:12,800
[SPEAKER_00] ili istjeruje zle duhove,

1380
00:58:12,800 --> 00:58:14,980
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, oni cijelovi se pitaju

1381
00:58:14,980 --> 00:58:15,860
[SPEAKER_00] ko si ti.

1382
00:58:15,860 --> 00:58:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ako si ti,

1383
00:58:17,340 --> 00:58:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] sjetite se ono kad kaže

1384
00:58:18,579 --> 00:58:19,719
[SPEAKER_00] ti si svetac Boži,

1385
00:58:19,719 --> 00:58:21,519
[SPEAKER_00] ti si, ok, možete sad reći,

1386
00:58:21,519 --> 00:58:23,699
[SPEAKER_00] pa dobro, ono kad ga Sotona napastuje,

1387
00:58:23,699 --> 00:58:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] tamo kaže,

1388
00:58:24,599 --> 00:58:26,039
[SPEAKER_00] ako si ti sin Boži,

1389
00:58:26,039 --> 00:58:27,579
[SPEAKER_00] baci se, je li tako i to?

1390
00:58:27,579 --> 00:58:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, pa kako onda Sotona nije znao

1391
00:58:29,500 --> 00:58:30,260
[SPEAKER_00] od koje je Isusu?

1392
00:58:30,260 --> 00:58:31,139
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, sin Boži.

1393
00:58:31,139 --> 00:58:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] Morate znati da naziv sin Boži

1394
00:58:33,079 --> 00:58:34,940
[SPEAKER_00] je bio naziv za svakog pomazanika,

1395
00:58:34,940 --> 00:58:36,980
[SPEAKER_00] ne za drugu božarsku osobu.

1396
00:58:36,980 --> 00:58:38,199
[SPEAKER_00] I za svakog pomazanika,

1397
00:58:38,199 --> 00:58:39,840
[SPEAKER_00] i za Davida se je reklo sin Boži,

1398
00:58:39,840 --> 00:58:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] i za Salomona se je reklo sin Boži,

1399
00:58:41,980 --> 00:58:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, za svakog pomazanika

1400
00:58:44,599 --> 00:58:45,480
[SPEAKER_00] to je bio naziv.

1401
00:58:45,480 --> 00:58:47,179
[SPEAKER_00] Za svakog mesiju,

1402
00:58:47,179 --> 00:58:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] mesijanskog lika, sin Boži.

1403
00:58:48,500 --> 00:58:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] Tako i ovdje.

1404
00:58:49,119 --> 00:58:50,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si ti kraljevskog roda,

1405
00:58:50,639 --> 00:58:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] ako si ti pomazanik mesija,

1406
00:58:52,059 --> 00:58:53,480
[SPEAKER_00] baci se, je li tako?

1407
00:58:53,480 --> 00:58:54,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ali imamo palo napavljene

1408
00:58:54,639 --> 00:58:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] da oni pred sobima samoga

1409
00:58:55,960 --> 00:58:57,139
[SPEAKER_00] utjelovljenog Boga.

1410
00:58:57,139 --> 00:59:00,780
[SPEAKER_00] I ona, kad istjeruje džavle,

1411
00:59:00,780 --> 00:59:02,139
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda oni kažu,

1412
00:59:02,139 --> 00:59:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] mi znamo od ko si ti,

1413
00:59:03,079 --> 00:59:03,980
[SPEAKER_00] i on ih ušutkava.

1414
00:59:03,980 --> 00:59:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] S razlogom ih ušutkava.

1415
00:59:05,500 --> 00:59:07,719
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, šutite, začepite,

1416
00:59:07,719 --> 00:59:08,199
[SPEAKER_00] čkomite,

1417
00:59:08,199 --> 00:59:09,219
[SPEAKER_00] ne smije se još znat.

1418
00:59:09,219 --> 00:59:11,139
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nemojte rešiti svojme šefu.

1419
00:59:11,199 --> 00:59:12,900
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, strah uz lih duhova

1420
00:59:12,900 --> 00:59:14,179
[SPEAKER_00] nisu rekli ni njemu.

1421
00:59:14,179 --> 00:59:16,900
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, sad malo karikiram.

1422
00:59:16,900 --> 00:59:17,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ali evo,

1423
00:59:17,659 --> 00:59:19,340
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ta važnost,

1424
00:59:19,340 --> 00:59:21,920
[SPEAKER_00] ta važnost da Boži plan spasenja

1425
00:59:21,920 --> 00:59:22,639
[SPEAKER_00] za čovjeka

1426
00:59:22,639 --> 00:59:24,320
[SPEAKER_00] bude potpuno skriven.

1427
00:59:24,320 --> 00:59:25,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nisu ga razumijeli

1428
00:59:25,800 --> 00:59:26,699
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi onoga vremena

1429
00:59:26,699 --> 00:59:27,860
[SPEAKER_00] i palo niti na pamet.

1430
00:59:27,860 --> 00:59:29,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je, zato je mnogima

1431
00:59:29,219 --> 00:59:30,699
[SPEAKER_00] i križ samlazan i tako dalje.

1432
00:59:30,699 --> 00:59:31,880
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, ni samome,

1433
00:59:31,880 --> 00:59:33,119
[SPEAKER_00] ni samome sotone.

1434
00:59:33,119 --> 00:59:34,500
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, samo ću s ovim,

1435
00:59:34,500 --> 00:59:35,800
[SPEAKER_00] ću zaključiti s ovim citatom

1436
00:59:35,800 --> 00:59:36,480
[SPEAKER_00] iz Kekica,

1437
00:59:36,480 --> 00:59:37,980
[SPEAKER_00] iz Katekizma Katoličke crkve.

1438
00:59:39,980 --> 00:59:40,940
[SPEAKER_00] 4.9.8

1439
00:59:40,940 --> 00:59:43,679
[SPEAKER_00] Šutnja evanđelja po Marku

1440
00:59:43,679 --> 00:59:45,179
[SPEAKER_00] i poslanica Novog Zavjeta

1441
00:59:45,179 --> 00:59:46,739
[SPEAKER_00] o Marijinom djevičanskom začeću

1442
00:59:46,739 --> 00:59:48,820
[SPEAKER_00] bila je kad i kad uzrokom nesigurnosti.

1443
00:59:48,820 --> 00:59:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mogu se pitati

1444
00:59:50,000 --> 00:59:51,760
[SPEAKER_00] nisu li posrijedi legende

1445
00:59:51,760 --> 00:59:52,659
[SPEAKER_00] ili teološke obrade

1446
00:59:52,659 --> 00:59:54,039
[SPEAKER_00] bez zahtjeva povjesnosti.

1447
00:59:54,039 --> 00:59:55,579
[SPEAKER_00] Na to valja odgovoriti.

1448
00:59:55,579 --> 00:59:57,019
[SPEAKER_00] Vjera u djevičansko začeće

1449
00:59:57,019 --> 00:59:58,099
[SPEAKER_00] Isusovo najlazila je

1450
00:59:58,099 --> 00:59:59,139
[SPEAKER_00] na živo protivljenje,

1451
00:59:59,139 --> 01:00:00,679
[SPEAKER_00] sarkazam i nesklačenje

1452
01:00:00,679 --> 01:00:02,380
[SPEAKER_00] nevjernika, židova i pogana.

1453
01:00:02,380 --> 01:00:03,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ona nije našla,

1454
01:00:03,639 --> 01:00:05,440
[SPEAKER_00] morate znati da se Sveti Jeronim,

1455
01:00:05,780 --> 01:00:06,719
[SPEAKER_00] Origen, isto tako.

1456
01:00:06,719 --> 01:00:08,179
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Jeronim je napisao

1457
01:00:08,179 --> 01:00:10,760
[SPEAKER_00] 500 stranica samo u onom

1458
01:00:10,760 --> 01:00:12,079
[SPEAKER_00] heosu, dok,

1459
01:00:12,079 --> 01:00:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] u priložnoj oznaci,

1460
01:00:13,559 --> 01:00:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] to je priložnoj oznaci vremena,

1461
01:00:15,380 --> 01:00:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] jer oni isto su kršani toga vremena,

1462
01:00:17,619 --> 01:00:19,159
[SPEAKER_00] imali iste stvari

1463
01:00:19,159 --> 01:00:21,599
[SPEAKER_00] i protivljena s kojima mi imamo i danas,

1464
01:00:21,599 --> 01:00:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] i argumente, i probleme,

1465
01:00:22,940 --> 01:00:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] i sarkazam i tome slično.

1466
01:00:24,900 --> 01:00:26,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ona nije našla motiva

1467
01:00:26,440 --> 01:00:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] u poganskoj mitologiji,

1468
01:00:27,639 --> 01:00:29,420
[SPEAKER_00] niti u kakvom prilagođavanju

1469
01:00:29,420 --> 01:00:30,219
[SPEAKER_00] idejama vremena.

1470
01:00:30,219 --> 01:00:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] Smisao toga događaja,

1471
01:00:31,500 --> 01:00:33,019
[SPEAKER_00] dok učiv je samo vjeri,

1472
01:00:33,019 --> 01:00:33,659
[SPEAKER_00] koja ga vidi

1473
01:00:33,659 --> 01:00:34,900
[SPEAKER_00] u one povezanosti

1474
01:00:34,900 --> 01:00:36,239
[SPEAKER_00] koja veže različite otajstva

1475
01:00:36,239 --> 01:00:36,820
[SPEAKER_00] međusobno,

1476
01:00:36,820 --> 01:00:38,300
[SPEAKER_00] u cijelini kristovih otajstava,

1477
01:00:38,300 --> 01:00:40,119
[SPEAKER_00] od utjelovljenja do paske,

1478
01:00:40,119 --> 01:00:41,539
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Ignacij Antiohijski,

1479
01:00:41,539 --> 01:00:43,400
[SPEAKER_00] već svjedoči takvu povezanost.

1480
01:00:43,400 --> 01:00:45,239
[SPEAKER_00] Poglavica ovoga svijeta

1481
01:00:45,239 --> 01:00:47,340
[SPEAKER_00] nije znao za Marino djevičanstvo

1482
01:00:47,340 --> 01:00:48,260
[SPEAKER_00] i njezin porod,

1483
01:00:48,619 --> 01:00:50,139
[SPEAKER_00] kao i za smrt gospodinovu,

1484
01:00:50,139 --> 01:00:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] tri vrhunska otajstva

1485
01:00:51,559 --> 01:00:52,780
[SPEAKER_00] koja se dogodiše

1486
01:00:52,780 --> 01:00:54,440
[SPEAKER_00] u Božjoj šutnji.

1487
01:00:54,440 --> 01:00:55,019
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno je.

1488
01:00:55,019 --> 01:00:56,960
[SPEAKER_00] I začeće u šutnji,

1489
01:00:56,960 --> 01:00:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] nije svijet zao za to.

1490
01:00:58,119 --> 01:00:59,539
[SPEAKER_00] I ruđenje u šutnji,

1491
01:00:59,539 --> 01:01:00,880
[SPEAKER_00] tamo u nekoj špilju u Betlehemu

1492
01:01:00,880 --> 01:01:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] i, dakle, samo raspeče

1493
01:01:03,460 --> 01:01:04,519
[SPEAKER_00] u šutnji,

1494
01:01:04,519 --> 01:01:05,400
[SPEAKER_00] izvan grada.

1495
01:01:05,400 --> 01:01:06,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, i jedan od kriminalaca.

1496
01:01:06,820 --> 01:01:08,480
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ga.

1497
01:01:08,480 --> 01:01:11,699
[SPEAKER_00] To je naš Sveti Josip.

1498
01:01:11,699 --> 01:01:13,039
[SPEAKER_00] On je čak odradio

1499
01:01:13,039 --> 01:01:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] i ovu jednu mističnu stvar,

1500
01:01:14,500 --> 01:01:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] a to je da je zaštitio,

1501
01:01:17,179 --> 01:01:18,699
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, čuvao u tajnosti,

1502
01:01:18,699 --> 01:01:20,860
[SPEAKER_00] Marino djevičansko začeće.

1503
01:01:20,860 --> 01:01:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ima li ko kakvo pitanje?

1504
01:01:23,500 --> 01:01:30,900
[SPEAKER_00] Moram čekati da se probujete prvo.

1505
01:01:30,900 --> 01:01:34,239
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je jasno.

1506
01:01:34,239 --> 01:01:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, dobro.

1507
01:01:34,920 --> 01:01:36,260
[SPEAKER_00] Sljedeći puta,

1508
01:01:36,260 --> 01:01:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] za mjesec dana,

1509
01:01:37,420 --> 01:01:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] razmišljajemo o Svetomljom.

1510
01:01:39,960 --> 01:01:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite da uvijek radite neki ili-ili.

1511
01:01:41,460 --> 01:01:43,099
[SPEAKER_00] Kao razbijamo neku staru sliku

1512
01:01:43,099 --> 01:01:44,480
[SPEAKER_00] i idemo prema nekoj novoj slici

1513
01:01:44,480 --> 01:01:46,420
[SPEAKER_00] i da ju biblijski podkrijepimo.

1514
01:01:46,940 --> 01:01:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] Sljedećeg puta možemo reći

1515
01:01:47,980 --> 01:01:49,920
[SPEAKER_00] da ćemo raditi o Svetom Josipu,

1516
01:01:49,920 --> 01:01:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] hraditelj ili po očim Isusov

1517
01:01:55,000 --> 01:01:58,099
[SPEAKER_00] ili konkretna slika Božjeg očinstva.

1518
01:01:58,099 --> 01:01:58,480
[SPEAKER_00] Jel?

1519
01:01:58,480 --> 01:01:59,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

1520
01:01:59,139 --> 01:02:00,420
[SPEAKER_00] Evo to mi ćemo.

